=== 評價 ===
對創作者吉利根來說，懷特的黑暗個性以及道德方面爭議，讓他在編寫劇情時很難下手，因此當《絕命毒師》要結束內容時，吉利根表示他不會特別在意播出，因為腦海不用去想懷特的事對他而言是某種解脫。<ref name="NYTimes"/>

媒體看法方面，《[[大西洋_(雜誌)|大西洋]]》雜誌認為懷特在過去就已經有著邪惡性格，患上癌症這件事只是加快暴露出他內心險惡一面的催化劑，而從染上重病那一刻起，便具備了會讓他轉變成一個怪物的所有因素。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2012/08/the-big-secret-of-breaking-bad-walter-white-was-always-a-bad-guy/261833/ |title=The Big Secret of 'Breaking Bad': Walter White Was Always a Bad Guy |work=[[大西洋_(雜誌)|大西洋]] |author=Scott Meslow |date=2012-08-31 |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2014-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140515174141/http://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2012/08/the-big-secret-of-breaking-bad-walter-white-was-always-a-bad-guy/261833/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>大眾文化網站Grantland表示懷特是《絕命毒師》裡最令人恐懼的存在，會導致面臨這種死亡與毀滅的局面並不是貪婪或癌症，而是沸騰的不滿怨恨。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://grantland.com/hollywood-prospectus/breaking-bad-season-5-episode-11-recap-cigs-lies-and-videotape-in-confessions/ |title=Breaking Bad Season 5, Episode 11 Recap: Cigs, Lies, and Videotape in 'Confessions' |work=Grantland |author=Andy Greenwald |date=2013-08-26 |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130085929/https://grantland.com/hollywood-prospectus/breaking-bad-season-5-episode-11-recap-cigs-lies-and-videotape-in-confessions/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

其它像《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》肯定吉利根在劇情裡把懷特演變成一個無情角色的安排，認為在此之前沒有人會願意把主角弄成讓人厭惡的角色，也沒有人能做到這一點。<ref name="HollyWoodReport"/>《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》則稱讚懷特的存在讓《絕命毒師》成為有史以來最了不起的戲劇作品，為我們觀賞的電視內容添增不少色彩。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/2013/08/08/bianco-combo-review-breaking-bad-and-low-winter-sun-august-9/2622023/ |title='Breaking Bad' review: Astonishing, again |work=[[今日美國|今日美國]] |author=Robert Bianco |date=2013-08-08 |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2013-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130810080144/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/2013/08/08/bianco-combo-review-breaking-bad-and-low-winter-sun-august-9/2622023/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 引用 ===
[[File:BCN_-_20150817_-_8_(21767191479).jpg|thumb]][[巴塞隆納|巴塞隆納]]一處有著華特·懷特[[街頭藝術|街頭塗鴉]]的門口。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.streetartutopia.com/?p=16130 |title=Walter White – By Axe Colours in Barcelona, Spain |work=Street Art Utopia |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2020-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722144748/https://www.streetartutopia.com/?p=16130 |dead-url=no }}</ref>]]
懷特在劇中的一些行為，有成為影迷模仿的對象。例如懷特在《絕命毒師》第三季第二集裡，有一段內容是懷特購買了一份[[披薩|披薩]]想對妻子史凱勒釋出善意，希望能獲得她的諒解；但在對方不領情後，便一氣之下將整個披薩甩到屋頂上。之後有不少影迷前往拍攝地點模仿懷特把披薩甩到屋頂上的橋段，造成該場景的實際屋主許多困擾，而讓吉利根不得不出面喊話請影迷停止該行為。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2015/tv/news/breaking-bad-house-pizzas-vince-gilligan-1201450839/ |title='Breaking Bad' Creator Urges Fans to Stop Throwing Pizzas on Walter White's Roof |work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]] |author=Seth Kelley |date=2015-03-11 |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2015-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151103114525/http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/breaking-bad-house-pizzas-vince-gilligan-1201450839/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://newscult.com/youre-not-walter-white-stop-throwing-pizza-roofs/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151125185246/http://newscult.com/youre-not-walter-white-stop-throwing-pizza-roofs/ |dead-url=yes |title=YOU'RE NOT WALTER WHITE, STOP THROWING PIZZA ON ROOFS |work=News Clut |author=Monica Adams |date=2013-10-21 |archivedate=2015-03-12 |accessdate=2020-07-22}}</ref>

另外在《絕命毒師》播完最後一集後不久，2013年10月4日有一群影迷在[[阿布奎基|阿布奎基]]當地報紙刊登了一份懷特的[[訃告|訃告]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.abqjournal.com/275038/it-provides-closure.html |title='Breaking Bad' Fan group places paid obituary for Walter White |work=Albuquerque Journal |author=Adrian Gomez |date=2013-10-05 |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506235415/https://www.abqjournal.com/275038/it-provides-closure.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>之後在19日演員傑克莫·布傑爾（Jackamoe Buzzell）{{noteTag|1=傑克莫·布傑爾之後有在《絕命毒師》的關聯影集《[[絕命律師|絕命律師]]》第三季裡演出。}}集合了影迷在阿布奎基舉辦懷特的喪禮遊行活動，其中靈車造型是採用懷特在劇中用來製造[[冰毒|冰毒]]的[[露營車|露營車]]。該活動之後在阿布奎基的「6855 4th St NW Los Ranchos」地址安置懷特的[[墓碑|墓碑]]，該墓碑上的照片則是採用克蘭斯頓飾演懷特的劇照。此活動所獲取超過3萬美元的參加費，都作為給當地關懷無家可歸民眾之慈善機構的募款。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2013/10/21/showbiz/tv/breaking-bad-funeral-walter-white/ |title='Breaking Bad': Walter White laid to rest with mock funeral |work=[[CNN|CNN]] |author=Breeanna Hare |date=2013-10-22 |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2021-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507131448/https://edition.cnn.com/2013/10/21/showbiz/tv/breaking-bad-funeral-walter-white |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/walter-white-laid-to-rest-in-breaking-bad-charity-funeral-20131021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023224144/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/walter-white-laid-to-rest-in-breaking-bad-charity-funeral-20131021 |dead-url=yes |title=Walter White Laid to Rest in 'Breaking Bad' Charity Funeral |work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]] |author=Kory Grow |date=2013-10-21 |archivedate=2013-10-23 |accessdate=2020-07-22}}</ref>

懷特也有被引用在一些大眾娛樂作品裡串場，例如由[[IDW公司|IDW]]發行的《[[忍者龜|忍者龜]]》第27期裡、或是《星戰毀滅者：機器人對喪屍》（Mars Attacks! Robots vs. Zombies）這些漫畫之中。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cbr.com/comic-book-easter-eggs-breaking-bad-easter-eggs/ |title=Comic Book Easter Eggs - Breaking Bad Easter Eggs! |work=Comic Book Resources |author=Brian Cronin |date=2014-09-09 |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021225903/https://www.cbr.com/comic-book-easter-eggs-breaking-bad-easter-eggs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>而克蘭斯頓也曾以懷特的身分在一些媒體上出現，像是2015年[[第四十九屆超級盃|第四十九屆超級盃]]比賽裡播放的一篇Esurance保險公司廣告，或是2016年12月10日的喜劇綜藝節目《[[週六夜現場|週六夜現場]]》，當時在節目上的笑料是懷特表示[[2016年美國總統選舉|新當選]]的美國總統[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]要提拔他為[[美國緝毒局|美國緝毒局]]負責人。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.comingsoon.net/tv/news/405605-walter-white-returns-in-extended-esurance-super-bowl-commercial |title=Walter White Returns in Extended Esurance Super Bowl Commercial |work=ComingSoon |author=Spencer Perry |date=2015-02-01 |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2015-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929123820/http://www.comingsoon.net/tv/news/405605-walter-white-returns-in-extended-esurance-super-bowl-commercial |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://time.com/4597357/donald-trump-walter-white-saturday-night-live/ |title=Donald Trump Picks Walter White to Head DEA on Saturday Night Live |work=[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]] |author=Mahita Gajanan |date=2016-12-11 |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126054945/https://time.com/4597357/donald-trump-walter-white-saturday-night-live/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 揣測 ==
《絕命毒師》播放結束後，不少影迷、媒體、或像是演員[[諾姆·麥克唐納|諾姆·麥克唐納]]等人，提出在最後一集裡懷特其實一開始就死在他偷來的[[富豪200系列|富豪200]]汽車裡，之後所發生的事，純粹是懷特腦海裡幻想的如此說法。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.vulture.com/2013/10/warren-ellis-breaking-bad-heisenberg-theory.html |title=Warren Ellis on Breaking Bad and the Horrible Glory of Heisenberg |work=Vulture |author=Warren Ellis |date=2013-10-02 |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2014-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110092341/http://www.vulture.com/2013/10/warren-ellis-breaking-bad-heisenberg-theory.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/daves4/was-the-breaking-bad-finale-all-just-a-fantasy-in-walter-whi |title=Was The "Breaking Bad" Finale All Just A Fantasy In Walter White's Head? |work=[[BuzzFeed|BuzzFeed]] |author=Dave Stopera |date=2013-10-03 |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2013-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204064134/http://www.buzzfeed.com/daves4/was-the-breaking-bad-finale-all-just-a-fantasy-in-walter-whi |dead-url=no }}</ref>而吉利根得知後駁斥了這樣的猜測內容，表示著如果這一切只是懷特死前腦海裡的一場夢，那懷特是不可能憑空知道他的學生平克曼有被囚禁一事。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/vince-gilligan-tackles-four-breaking-648899 |title=Vince Gilligan Tackles Four 'Breaking Bad' Myths |work=好萊塢報導 |author=Aaron Couch |date=2013-10-16 |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2014-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140120085817/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/vince-gilligan-tackles-four-breaking-648899 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

